View a Model

You can view a model deployed in your org.

View a Prediction Definition in Model Manager.
The Overview tab displays one or more models associated with the selected prediction definition.

COLUMN	DESCRIPTION
Model Name	Name of the model. Click to view the model.
Status	Indicates whether the model is active (Enabled) or not (Disabled).
Rank	Order in which models are executed under a prediction, with 1 being the first to execute.
Algorithm	Algorithm used to create this model.
Accuracy	Logistic models only. Cumulative total accuracy for this model.
RMSE	Linear models only. RMSE (Root Mean Squared Error) for this model.
Alerts	Number of alerts associated with the model.
# of Predictions	Total number of predictions made by this model within the org.
Model Deployed	Date and time when the model was deployed.
Creator	User who created the model.

To view details for a particular model, click its Model Name, or choose View Model Details from the dropdown.
